name: Save My Musik
tag_list: music-storage, cloud-computing, online-music, music-management, music-streaming, music, playlists
overview:
Save My Musik is an entirely cloud based, personal musik management website. The company goal is to provide a hassle-free musik storage and streaming experience anytime, anywhere.

Users can easily organise and manage their own musik files and playlists saving hours of management headaches while protecting them from potential data loss. Users can select a low-end storage plan, and as their musik collection grows can easily upgrade the size of their account. There is a free 7-day service test drive.

The company also provides various partnering opportunities with site content providers, artists and copyright owners.
